Alembic migrations.

Generate the initial migration after spinning up the dev DB:

    $env:DATABASE_URL="postgresql+psycopg://warn:warn@localhost:5432/warn_v2"
    uv run alembic revision --autogenerate -m "initial schema"
    uv run alembic upgrade head

For tests we bypass migrations and use `Base.metadata.create_all(engine)` against
an in-memory SQLite — see `tests/conftest.py`.
